# ðŸ˜Š Sentiment Analysis Web Application  
*A simple Flask-powered web app for analyzing text sentiment using TextBlob.*

---

## ðŸš€ Project Overview
This web application allows users to input any text and instantly get:
- **Sentiment (Positive / Negative / Neutral)**
- **Polarity Score** (ranges from -1 to 1)
- **Subjectivity Score** (ranges from 0 to 1)

Built using:
- **Flask** (Backend Web Framework)  
- **TextBlob** (Natural Language Processing Library)

---

##  Features

### âœ” Interactive Web Form  
